{"article_id":"J65akNmiQ9Tt8YVC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Paris , France","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"( CNN )","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"French authorities took the offensive Wednesday ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"raiding a purported hideout of the suspected ringleader in last week 's deadly Paris attacks in an operation","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that ended with eight detained ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"two dead and potentially more bloodshed thwarted .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"At one point , authorities believe","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"he was holed up on the third floor of an apartment building in the northern Paris suburb of Saint-Denis ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Paris prosecutor Francois Molins said Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Whether he was there","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"when scores of heavily armed French police launched their assault at 4:20 a.m. Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"( 10:20 p.m . ET Tuesday )","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"is unknown .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Some residents in the area told CNN","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"they saw Abaaoud recently in the neighborhood and at a local mosque .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Investigators zeroed in on the building","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"after picking up phone conversations","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"indicating","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that a relative of Abaaoud might be there .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"They met fierce resistance from the start , including an armored door , a woman","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"who blew herself up","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and bullets","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"flying back and forth for about an hour .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"The French officers even used powerful munitions ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"which led to one floor of the building collapsing .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"That violence produced rubble","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that included body parts ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"on which investigators are conducting DNA tests .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Neither Abaaoud nor suspect Salah Abdeslam ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"for whom authorities have been hunting since the attacks ,","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"were among those detained in the operation ,","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Molins said .","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"French President Francois Hollande held up the vicious back-and-forth as further proof","depth":4},{"id":33,"text":"that `` we are at war '' with ISIS .","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"`` What the terrorists were targeting was what France represents .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"This is what was attacked on the night of November 13 , ''","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"`` These barbarians targeted France 's diversity .","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"It was the youth of France","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"who were targeted","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"simply because they represent life . ''","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"ISIS first drew international attention","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"for taking over swaths of Iraq and Syria ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"leaving a trail of violence and destruction in its wake .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"And its efforts","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"to bring terror to the global stage","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"seem to be growing .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"This month alone , ISIS has claimed responsibility for the Paris attacks , the downing of a Russian passenger jet in Egypt and a pair of suicide bombings in Beirut .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"France had already been part of the U.S.-led coalition","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"fighting ISIS with airstrikes .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"But the country has stepped up its efforts since the series of shootings and explosions in Paris last week ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"which killed 129 people .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Now , Hollande has proposed extending France 's state of emergency for three more months","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"-- a measure","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"that , among other things , gives authorities greater powers","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"in conducting searches , holding people","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"and dissolving certain groups .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"To go after the Islamist extremist group ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"the French President also said","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"he would appeal to world leaders","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"-- including meeting next week with U.S. President Barack Obama and Russian President Vladimir Putin ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"who have been at odds on what to do in Syria .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"`` There is no more ... divide .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"There are only men and women of duty , ''","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"`` We must destroy this army","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that menaces the entire world , not just some countries . ''","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Whoever was inside the Saint-Denis apartment on Wednesday appeared to be `` prepared to act '' in possibly another attack ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Molins said ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"noting their weaponry , structured organization and determination .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Some 110 police swarmed on the diverse , working-class area","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"that is home to the Stade de France sports stadium ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"where three suicide bombings took place days earlier .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"They first went into one apartment","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that had been under surveillance since Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"a Paris police source said .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"Explosions heard at scene of Paris suburb raid","depth":6},{"id":78,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Explosions heard at scene of Paris suburb raid","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"02:26","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Telephone communications on a wiretap by French and Belgian security agencies indicated","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"a woman at the residence was Abaaoud 's cousin ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"a Belgian counterterrorism official told CNN .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"That raid led them to another apartment on the same street .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Molins described it as a complex operation .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"For almost an hour ,","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"there was uninterrupted gunfire","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"as police tried to get into the apartment .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"The violent standoff left residents in the area ,","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"already shaken by last week 's attacks ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"startled and scared .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"`` We could see the bullets , ''","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"a woman ,","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"who identified herself only as Sabrine ,","depth":15},{"id":97,"text":"told CNN affiliate France 2 .","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"`` We could feel the building shaking . ''","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"Three people in the Saint-Denis building itself ,","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"including one with a bullet wound in the arm ,","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"are among the eight detained ,","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"according to Molins .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"The others include the person","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"who loaned the apartment to the suspected terrorists and his friend .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"Two of the eight held were hospitalized ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"Interior Ministry spokesman Pierre-Henry Brandet told France Info radio .","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Saadana Aymen , a 29-year-old","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"who lives one street down ,","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"could n't believe","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"what was happening in his neighborhood .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"`` When you think of Saint-Denis ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"you do n't think of terrorists , ''","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"he told CNN .","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"`` I 'm shocked !","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Why would the terrorists pick this neighborhood ? ''","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"That was n't the only place","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"where French authorities fanned out Tuesday night into Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":118,"text":"as they worked to find suspects","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"tied to the attacks","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"and cracked down on security .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"The Interior Ministry announced","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"118 searches led to the detention of at least 25 people , the confiscation of 34 weapons and the discovery of illicit drugs in 16 instances .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"In recent days , hundreds of similar operations have been conducted ,","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"the ministry said ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"resulting in 64 people being held","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"and 118 put under house arrest .","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Authorities have not provided details about the arrests","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"or said","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"what connection they could have to Friday 's attacks .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Molins said","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"investigators are working to piece together where terrorists were in the days and hours","depth":7},{"id":132,"text":"leading up to the attacks","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"-- and with whom they had contact .","depth":6},{"id":134,"text":"They 've encountered at least one piece of evidence","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"that could help them in their search :","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"One of the attacker 's cell phones was found in a trash bin outside the Bataclan theater ,","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"where most of Friday 's victims were gunned down .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"A message on the phone ,","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"according to Molins ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"said ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"`` Here we go ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"it 's starting . ''","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"Authorities are trying to determine who the message was sent to ,","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"And they 're still trying to determine","depth":6},{"id":146,"text":"whether the suspected ringleader in the attack is still on the run ,","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"or whether his remains were found in the rubble .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":295,"left":188,"right":294,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":179,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":175,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":160,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":149,"right":159,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":152,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":2,"right":151,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":3,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":154,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":9,"right":156,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":155,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"restatement","